
This is a demo to learn about localStorage and Offline API of HTML5.

I would like to make a very simple app to change have notes with or without internet.

When the browser is online, if have omething on localStorage goes using JSON to a MySQL database and clean localStorage.

When the browser is offline,add some data to localstorage.

Use the code as you want but respect the author putting my authority! If there are any questios, email me!

